/blockquote><br />\n中華民國咪台灣囉，係咁架啦"},{"pid":"92e72a7c88bfa2004af8bf3e76a6735fca40d08c","tid":48535,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實台灣人有冇諗過收復中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係想自己獨立算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國又唔係台灣一部份 <br />\n點解要收復？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中華民國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n中華民國咪台灣囉，係咁架啦</blockquote><br />\n睇番中華民國憲法 領土範圍係無台澎(五五憲章)"},{"pid":"c8a3812ee77b7a26462a6c743f01e4d57eec8941","tid":48535,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:41:23.000Z","msg":"當你見到十幾億似人非人嘅生物係到進行各種種族滅絕行為，你寧願乖乖留係台灣定接收佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4918f011d41cf485836addc6628308ed9c3375","tid":48535,"uid":36585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實台灣人有冇諗過收復中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係想自己獨立算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國又唔係台灣一部份 <br />\n點解要收復？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中華民國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n中華民國咪台灣囉，係咁架啦</blockquote><br />\n睇番中華民國憲法 領土範圍係無台澎(五五憲章)</blockquote><br />\n咁講中華民國咪得返金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d539162c3ffc445ec2b393be95d32ebb8e779b","tid":48535,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實台灣人有冇諗過收復中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係想自己獨立算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國又唔係台灣一部份 <br />\n點解要收復？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中華民國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n中華民國咪台灣囉，係咁架啦</blockquote><br />\n睇番中華民國憲法 領土範圍係無台澎(五五憲章)</blockquote><br />\n咁講中華民國咪得返金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n金馬屬於福建省<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美在台協會前處長司徒文：美國過去「一個中國」政策是錯的<br />\n<br />\n2016-12-05 11:35<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國準總統川普與我國總統蔡英文在電話中討論台美事務，引起全球關注，美國在台協會（AIT）台北辦事處前處長司徒文（William Stanton）對此表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">美國過去「一個中國」的政策是錯的，而且他強調美國從來都沒講過中國擁有台灣的主權。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由媒體人周玉蔻主持的《蔻蔻早餐》廣播節目，今日以電話連線訪問了司徒文，訪問他對於川蔡熱線的看法。司徒文首先表示，這應該是川普幕僚作出的計畫與建議，而不是台灣單方面的行動，他認為這是一個很正面的事情，也強調美國早就該做了。<br />\n<br />\n司徒文還說「一個中國」的政策是有問題的，美國方面從未講過中國對台灣擁有主權。司徒文最後提醒，這個溝通的管道既然達成了，那麼可以繼續努力維持並提升，畢竟這是過去馬政府想要做卻沒做到的事情。<br />\n(自由時報)"},{"pid":"4f2b497bdb630c8f504a3197792ea85c2479f141","tid":48535,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf4993e55b2352759929c815dc7f6a6cc65734c","tid":48535,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4d1cd23f0a3ad58d543010445e6484b9855f1b","tid":48535,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:19:01.000Z","msg":"respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57eb944dc9261d99d1abecb8622ed7584b9452a0","tid":48535,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實台灣人有冇諗過收復中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係想自己獨立算<